## Cross-Spoke Communication

**Signal Flow:**
1. Spoke publishes high-impact decision (impact >= 8)
2. Signal written to hub/intake/
3. hub-watcher notifies other spokes on their next session_start
4. Spokes acknowledge or adopt the pattern

**Example signals:**
- Authentication pattern changes
- New architectural decisions
- Performance optimizations discovered
- Bug patterns and fixes

